caption: Recovering from a bad Apply
tags: $:/plugins/crosseye/json-convert/usage/recipes
title: $:/plugins/crosseye/json-convert/usage/recipes/recover-apply
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

The ''Imported this session'' list at the bottom of the Console is your
undo log.  Click a title to navigate to it; delete or edit as needed.
The list is per-session — on reload it's empty.  For longer-term tracking,
consider tagging imported tiddlers (via a binding in the profile, e.g.
`"tags": "Imported {{...}}"`) so you can filter for them later.
